metadata.name: Morphy
metadata.description: Hi. My name is Morphy. I have 5 pets. Love video games and my mom. I have 3 sisters aand 62 brothes. Sometimes I fell myself lonely because we came here after was started. We felt like stranger a little bit because we dont know how to use cars here and we need to take passpors and we have some problems with this on Earth. soo... hope to go to Earth school this year and meet some friends. but mostly I want to come back home.
